   462	One final verdict line exactly as REVIEW_VERDICT: PASS or REVIEW_VERDICT: FAIL.
   463	Then bullets prefixed [BLOCKER], [HIGH], [MED], or [LOW].
   464	PROMPT_TEXT
   465	)"
